    <note>Wu(3) Zong [22404] Liangchao beiyao, pp. 481 ff. gives biography and kinship. When he was demoted to Chuzhou tuanlian fushi in 1207, he was espcially granted permission to live in any prefecture of Jinghu or Guangnan of his choice--but apparently forbidden to return to Sichuan, probably owing to the crimes of his kin, Xi [4013]. SHY:ZG, 72.29b, 74.14a-14b, 25a. CBD, 2, 1130.From Hartwell's ACTIVITY table:1181:  Demoted one grade and dismissed (fangba) as Tiju Sichuan chama si1203:  As new Sichuan chama, he was given another commission1207:  Former Sichuan Duda chama, was demoted to Chuzhou tuanlian fushi and banished from Sichuan</note>
